divs: Sighting DetailsI was walking my dog in our yard which is lighted, saw a light & looked up to see two large circles of bright light over my tree line, one seemed to jump the other--did this about three times then disappeared as if a light had been turned off.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Tightwad
